author: Picquart Pierre
title: Picquart Pierre
text: Beautiful experience! For two years, In France, I was looking for an international web agency able to make a beautifull and professional website pierrepicquart.eu. I found it ! I am very satisfied. Very nice people, very competitive price, requested updates (colors, updated photos, videos and text....), project very well follow-up, many personal adjustment of the site, good others advices, usefull chat everyday, I recommend 100%!
